================================================================================
SUMMARY OF MODIFICATIONS (per Apache 2.0 §4(b))
================================================================================

Files added by Lucilead:

    src/core/prompts/system-prompt/claude-code-loader.ts
        Auto-loads ~/CLAUDE.md and an "always-on terse voice" directive into
        every session's system prompt.

    src/core/prompts/system-prompt/memory-loader.ts
        Auto-loads the user's Claude-Code-style memory index from
        ~/.claude/projects/-Users-<user>/memory/MEMORY.md.

    src/core/prompts/system-prompt/tools/llm_relay.ts
    src/core/task/tools/handlers/LLMRelayToolHandler.ts
        New `llm_relay` tool that delegates work to external LLMs (GPT,
        Gemini, Grok) via the user's local relay CLI.

    src/core/usage/pricing.ts
    src/core/usage/UsageTracker.ts
    src/core/usage/error-classifier.ts
        Cross-provider token-spend tracking, per-provider budgets, drain
        alerts, classification of known API errors with fallback hints.

    src/hosts/vscode/cline-cc-status-bar.ts
        VS Code status bar item showing live spend.

    webview-ui/src/components/chat/task-header/buttons/SettingsGearButton.tsx
        Per-chat settings gear that opens the auto-approve modal.

Files modified by Lucilead:

    src/shared/tools.ts
        Added LLM_RELAY tool enum value.

    src/core/assistant-message/index.ts
        Added `model`, `prompt_file`, `output_file` to toolParamNames.

    src/core/prompts/system-prompt/index.ts
        getSystemPrompt now appends CLAUDE.md and memory index.

    src/core/prompts/system-prompt/tools/init.ts
        Registers llm_relay tool variants.

    src/core/prompts/system-prompt/variants/*/config.ts (12 files)
        Added LLM_RELAY to each variant's tool list.

    src/core/task/tools/ToolExecutorCoordinator.ts
        Registers LLMRelayToolHandler.

    src/core/task/index.ts
        onUsageChunk now forwards to UsageTracker; failed-API-request path
        appends classifier-derived fallback hints.

    src/core/slash-commands/index.ts
    src/core/prompts/commands.ts
    src/shared/slashCommands.ts
        Added /remember slash command for end-of-task memory write-back.

    src/integrations/checkpoints/CheckpointUtils.ts
        Per-path approval prompt for checkpoints in normally-protected dirs
        (Desktop, Documents, Downloads, home), persisted to
        ~/.claude/lucibuild-checkpoint-allowlist.json.

    src/extension.ts
        Registers the LuciBuild status bar in activate().

    package.json, README.md
        Renamed from "Cline" to "LuciBuild"; metadata updated.

================================================================================
TELEMETRY
================================================================================

Upstream Cline ships with optional PostHog telemetry. LuciBuild defaults this
OFF; users may explicitly opt in via the standard Cline telemetry setting if
they choose. No data is sent to Lucilead servers from this extension.

